  "_doc": "Pinned per-metric scorecard-debt baseline for the unified control pane. total_debt is the raw-unit ratchet gate; grade_debt is the scale-invariant severity companion, and grade_weights pins each metric letter-grade severity so an A->B slip reds the gate even at flat raw debt (#1423). The raw-debt floor (metrics/total_debt) is held conservatively; grade_weights are pinned at the current at-or-below grade read. Re-pin after a debt drop to ratchet the trend down: python tools/scorecard_control_pane.py --pin",
